title: BRIEF-Valeura Energy Says Positive Production Test Results At Inanli-1

BRIEF-Valeura Energy Says Positive Production Test Results At Inanli-1

Stock Markets 30 minutes ago (Sep 05, 2019 02:40)

© Reuters. BRIEF-Valeura Energy Says Positive Production Test Results At Inanli-1 Sept 5 (Reuters) - Valeura Energy Inc : * VALEURA ENERGY INC. - POSITIVE PRODUCTION TEST RESULTS AT INANLI-1 * VALEURA ENERGY INC - ANNOUNCE A SUCCESSFUL NATURAL GAS FLOW TEST FROM SECOND STIMULATED ZONE IN INANLI-1 APPRAISAL WELL * VALEURA ENERGY INC - VALEURA AND ITS PARTNER EQUINOR DECIDED TO ADD AN ADDITIONAL TEST ZONE TO INANLI-1 WORK PROGRAMME * VALEURA ENERGY INC - TESTING IN INANLI-1 IS EXPECTED TO EXTEND INTO IN Q4 2019 WITH ALL TESTS FULLY FUNDED BY EQUINOR

BRIEF-Valeura Energy Says Positive Production Test Results At Inanli-1
